        <p>Covid pauremic ne sirf health ko nahi, baalon ko also bahut nuksaan pahunchaya. Lakhs of people worldwide ne covid ke baad extreme hair fall experience ofya. Aur India mein toh ye problem and widespread thi — high fever ke cases, stress, lockdown of tension, and nutrition of kami — sab milke baalon of band baja di.</p>

