<p>Especially for the <strong>Indian climate and lifestyle</strong>, maintaining healthy hair and skin requires specialized care that addresses local environmental factors, diet, and genetics.</p>

<h2>Kyun fall Rahe Hain hair Covid Ke Baad? — Science Samjhein</h2>
        <p>Post-covid hair fall ka main reason hai <strong>Telogen Effluvium</strong>. Ye ek condition hai jismein body ke extreme stress ya shock of wajah from baalon ke growth cycle mein disruption hota hai.</p>

        <h3>Normal Hair Cycle vs Post-Covid Disruption:</h3>
        <p>Normal situation mein sirf 10-15% hair Telogen (resting) phafrom mein happen. Baof 85-90% Anagen (growth) phafrom mein happen. Post-covid mein what/can hota hai of body ke extreme stress responfrom from <strong>30-50% hair ek saath Telogen phafrom mein chale jaate hain</strong>. 2-3 months baad ye sab hair ek saath girte hain — isliye achanak bahut zyada hair fall hota hai.</p>

        <h3>Covid Hair Fall Ke Specific Triggers:</h3>
        <p><strong>High fever:</strong> 100+ degree fever body ke liye major stress hai. Ye sabfrom strong trigger hai Telogen Effluvium ka. <strong>Inflammatory responfrom:</strong> Covid fromvere inflammation cause karta hai jo directly follicles affect karta hai. Cytokine storm follicles ko damage kar sakta hai. <strong>Medications:</strong> Covid treatment mein use hone wali medicines (steroids, antivirals) hair cycle disrupt kar sakti hain. <strong>Nutritional depletion:</strong> Fighting covid body ke nutrient stores — especially iron, zinc, Vitamin D — deplete karta hai. <strong>Emotional stress:</strong> Fear, anxiety, isolation — ye sab emotional triggers also contribute karte hain. <strong>Low oxygen levels:</strong> Reduced oxygen supply follicles ko directly affect karta hai.</p>

        
