        <p>Ye samajhna zaroori hai of post-covid hair fall of ek specific pattern hoti hai:</p>

        <p><strong>Covid recovery (Week 0):</strong> Fever utri, energy wapas aa rahi hai. hair normal lag rahe hain abhi. Body andar from stressed hai lekin externally sab theek dikhta hai. <strong>Month 1-2 post-recovery:</strong> Thoda zyada hair girne lag sakte hain lekin dramatic nahi. Most log notice also nahi karte is phafrom mein. <strong>Month 2-3 post-recovery (Peak shedding):</strong> Achanak bahut zyada hair girne lagte hain. Comb mein, shower mein, pillow pe — har jagah hair. <strong>Ye sabfrom scary phafrom hai lekin ye normal hai.</strong> Din mein 200-300+ hair also gir sakte hain. <strong>Month 3-6 post-recovery:</strong> Gradually shedding reduce honi chahiye. Agar reduce nahi ho rahi toh prkiessional evaluation zaroori hai. <strong>Month 6-12 post-recovery:</strong> New hair growth visible hoga. Baby hairs dikhenge. Recovery phafrom — patience chahiye.</p>

        <h2>Step-by-Step Recovery Plan — Covid Ke Baad hair Bachayein</h2>

        <h3>Step 1: Panic Mat do — Stress Hair Fall Aur Badhaata Hai</h3>
        <p>Ye sabfrom pehla and sabfrom important step hai. Post-covid hair fall dekhke log bahut stress mein aa jaate hain — and ye additional stress hair fall ko and badha deta hai. Ek vicious cycle ban jaata hai. Yaad rakhein — Telogen Effluvium <strong>temporary hai</strong>. hair wapas aayenge. Follicles dead nahi hain, sirf resting phafrom mein hain. Almost sabhi post-covid hair loss patients recover karte hain.</p>

        <h3>Step 2: Nutrition Recovery Plan — Body Ko Rebuild do</h3>
        <p>Covid body ke nutrient stores bahut deplete karta hai. Pehla kaam hai in stores ko wapas bharana.</p>

        <p><strong>Priority 1 — Iron:</strong> Post-covid iron levels bahut gir jaate hain. Palak, beetroot, dates, pomegranate roz khayein. Iron supplement doctor of advice from lein (sirf agar blood test mein low aaye). Vitamin C ke saath lein for 67% better absorption.</p>

        <p><strong>Priority 2 — Vitamin D:</strong> Covid and lockdown dono Vitamin D deplete karte hain. 15-20 minutes sunlight daily (morning best hai). Supplement: 1000-2000 IU daily (after blood test). Fortified milk and fatty fish add do diet mein.</p>

        <p><strong>Priority 3 — Zinc:</strong> Zinc immune recovery and hair growth dono ke liye critical hai. Pumpkin fromeds, chickpeas, yogurt, cashews daily khayein. Supplement: 15-30mg daily (doctor of advice from).</p>

        <p><strong>Priority 4 — Protein:</strong> Body ko rebuilding ke liye extra protein chahiye. Daily 60-70g protein target do. Eggs, chicken, fish, paneer, dal, soyabean. Har meal mein protein source hona chahiye.</p>

        <p><strong>Priority 5 — Biotin & B-Complex:</strong> B vitamins energy recovery and hair growth dono mein help karte hain. Almonds, walnuts, eggs, whole grains. B-complex supplement helpful hai post-covid.</p>

        <p>Detailed nutrition guidance ke liye hamari <a href="vitamins-nutrition-healthy-hair.php">complete vitamins and nutrition guide</a> padhein.</p>

        <h3>Step 3: Gentle Hair Care — Baalon Ko Zyada Damage Mat Dein</h3>
        <p>Post-covid phafrom mein hair already weak hain. Inhe extra gentle care chahiye.</p>

        <p><strong>Gentle washing:</strong> Sulfate-free shampoo use do. Alternate days wash do (roz nahi). Lukewarm water — na hot, na cold. <strong>No heat, no chemicals:</strong> Straightener, blow dryer, curling iron — sab band. Coloring, bleaching, rebonding — reduce from reduce 6 months wait do. <strong>Gentle haurling:</strong> Wide-tooth comb only. Wet hair mein kabhi comb mat do. Towel from gently pat dry — rubbing nahi. <strong>Lokirom hairstyles:</strong> Tight ponytails avoid do. Silk pillowcafrom use do — friction reduce hoti hai. hair khule ya lokirom braid mein rakhein.</p>

