        <h2>Post-Covid Hair Fall vs Other Conditions — Kaifrom Pehchanein?</h2>
        <p>Kabhi kabhi jo hair loss "post-covid" lag raha hai, wo actually kuch and also ho sakta hai. Covid sometimes underlying conditions trigger ya expkirom kar deta hai:</p>

        <p><strong>Thyroid issues:</strong> Covid thyroid function disrupt kar sakta hai. Agar hair fall ke saath weight changes, fatigue, cold fromnsitivity ho — thyroid test zaroor karwayein. <strong>Iron deficiency anemia:</strong> Covid pehle from existing mild deficiency ko fromvere bana deta hai. Fatigue, pale skin, breathlessness ke saath hair fall — CBC and ferritin test karwayein. <strong>Androgenetic alopecia triggered by covid:</strong> Kuch logon mein covid genetic hair loss ko "activate" ya accelerate kar deta hai. Agar hair fall ek specific pattern mein hai (receding hairline, crown thinning) — ye post-covid Telogen Effluvium from different hai. <strong>Alopecia Areata:</strong> Rare cases mein covid ke baad immune system follicles attack karna shuru kar deta hai. Patchy bald spots dikhein toh immediately doctor from milein.</p>

        <p>Agar aapko doubt hai of ye sirf post-covid hai ya kuch and also toh zaroor <a href="../contact.php">prkiessional consultation lein</a>. Blood tests and trichoscopy from exact diagnosis hogi.</p>

